    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm looking to find a new home for my car. It's been a fantastic, reliable ride and is still in really solid shape for its next owner. It's been well-cared for and drives like a charm\u2014perfect for someone who wants a dependable vehicle that still looks great on the driveway. I've absolutely loved driving this beauty, but it's time for someone else to enjoy it. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to take it for a spin!",
