    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically robust E46 M3, powered by the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. This driver\u2019s example has been meticulously maintained, with critical subframe reinforcement completed and a cooling system overhaul for thermal efficiency. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile engagement, paired with a factory-spec limited-slip differential for optimal power delivery. The chassis remains composed thanks to refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers, preserving the E46\u2019s renowned steering feedback and lateral grip. A well-sorted machine ready for the twisties or the occasional track day.",
      "price": 34500.0,
