    {
      "id": "sybil_17_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_17",
      "description": "This vehicle is a fantastic example of a well-maintained daily driver that balances performance with everyday utility. The exterior finish retains a high gloss, though close inspection reveals minor road-derived stone chips on the front fascia and a small scuff on the rear bumper consistent with careful use. Inside, the cabin is remarkably clean and has been kept smoke-free; the premium upholstery shows only light creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster, with all other seating surfaces appearing firm and intact. Mechanically, the car is robust. It has followed a strict maintenance schedule, including a recent comprehensive fluid service and brake pad replacement. The engine pulls smoothly, and the transmission shifts with precision. All onboard electronics, from the dual-zone climate control to the premium sound system, are fully operational. This is a dependable, honest car that offers a refined driving experience for its next owner.",
